		5.2 Saving the content of the key into a file, name it cs615-hw2-key.pem

			$ vim ~/.ec2/cs615-hw2-key.pem

		5.3 Changing the permission of the key file to 400.

			$ chmod 400 ~/.ec2/cs615-hw2-key.pem

	6. Running a new instance for Fedora Core 8.

		$ ec2-run-instances ami-b232d0db -k cs615-hw2-key -g cs615-hw2-group -t t1.micro
