Install pkgsrc and the same packages

	1. Install pkgsrc

		# wget ftp://ftp.netbsd.org/pub/pkgsrc/pkgsrc-2011Q4/pkgsrc-2011Q4.tar.gz
		# tar zxvf pkgsrc-2011Q4.tar.gz
		# cd pkgsrc/bootstrap
		# yum install gcc
		# ./bootstrap

	2. Build binary packages

		Please remember to add /usr/pkg/bin to your PATH environment variable
		and /usr/pkg/man to your MANPATH environment variable, if necessary.

		# export PATH=/usr/pkg/bin:$PATH

		2.1 gcc

